The paper focuses on generating accurate and flexible sentences to describe remote sensing images, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) techniques. The paper also mentions the construction of a large-scale data set, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of annotated instructions to better describe remote sensing images, which could relate to information retrieval (cs.IR) as well.
